{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75fbd9ba6d","title":"孤立傅作义部于集宁后再齐灭之","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9eccb2b32","index":0,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":24,"articleId":"75fbd9ba6d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a915ad26e8","type":"paragraph","text":"孤立傅作义部于集宁后再齐灭之”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"75fbd9ba6d"},{"id":"5bba0d034f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年10月24日）录、贺：如博·部主力固守集宁，一时不能攻克，望集中主力歼灭十八台、卓资山、三道营、旗下营、白塔之敌，占领集宁、归缓间二百余里铁路，发动群众建立政权，收集粮食，使集宁博部陷于孤立，然后歼灭之。此办法是否可行，望考虑电告。如集宁可能攻克，开灭得部主力，则不必变更部署。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"75fbd9ba6d"},{"id":"e9fd9c1711","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"75fbd9ba6d"},{"id":"915646f089","type":"paragraph","text":"西敬[I]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋察冀军区司令员兼政治委员基荣臻和晋缓军区司令员贺龙的电报[2]傅，指售作义，当时任国民党军第十二战区司令长官。[3]均为平续线上集宁与归绥问的村镇。十八台、三道营、旗下营属卓资县。卓资山，镇名，今为内蒙古卓资县县治。白塔，属今内蒙古呼和浩特。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"75fbd9ba6d"}],"page":{"id":"bb72af7a07","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"75fbd9ba6d","start":468,"end":468}}}},"__N_SSG":true}